WEBVTT

00:00.591 --> 00:03.047
This is the Financial News Network, I'm Stephanie Shyu.

00:03.163 --> 00:07.211
Sbarro said that it is filing for Chapter 11 bankruptcy protection...

00:07.531 --> 00:09.745
...as it looks for restructure on Monday.

00:10.060 --> 00:13.283
The chain has suffered since consumers reduced spending in the recession.

00:13.472 --> 00:17.488
It was also hurt due to the fact that many restaurant locations are in retail malls...

00:17.574 --> 00:20.892
...where shoppers avoided during the economic downturn.

00:21.013 --> 00:27.003
Sbarro's also hurt by debt that it took on when private equity firm MidOcean Partners bought it in January.

00:27.096 --> 00:34.483
It has total assets of about 471 million dollars and about 486.6 million dollars in debt according to the bankruptcy filing.

00:35.031 --> 00:38.628
For further updates on this story and more, stay tuned to the Financial News Network.

00:38.797 --> 00:39.681
I'm Stephanie Shyu.

